# Direction Fabric dogfooding policy.
#
# One sentence rule: commit project direction, not agent runtime state.
#
# Track durable repo protocol and direction:
# - AGENTS.md
# - .fabric/config.yaml
# - .fabric/ledger/events.jsonl (candidate/durable project direction only)
# - .agents/skills/**
#
# Keep per-thread local state, generated checkpoints, and the git-common
# shared mirror out of Git.
.fabric/active/
.fabric/generated/
.fabric/ledger/threads.jsonl
